, and cellular and tissue-based products. The company sells its products through direct or distributor sales representatives, as well as hip and knee products through independent sales agents. Globus Medical, Inc. was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Audubon, Pennsylvania.", "fullTimeEmployees": 5300, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. David C. Paul", "age": 57, "title": "Co-Founder & Executive Chairman", "yearBorn": 1967, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 1486468, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 21754196}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Daniel T. Scavilla", "age": 59, "title": "President, CEO & Director", "yearBorn": 1965, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 1921774, "exercisedValue": 8224800, "unexercisedValue": 4376843}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Keith W. Pfeil", "age": 45, "title": "CFO & COO", "yearBorn": 1979, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 1104613, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 1900186}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Kelly G. Huller Esq.", "age": 52, "title": "Executive VP, General Counsel & Corporate Secretary", "yearBorn": 1972, "fiscalYear": 2024, "totalPay": 789513, "exercisedValue": 1031450, "unexercisedValue": 4991818}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Brian J. Kearns", "age": 57, "title": "Senior Vice President of Business Development & Investor Relations", "yearBorn": 1967, "fiscalYear": 2024, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}], "auditRisk": 7, "boardRisk": 9, "compensationRisk": 6, "shareHolderRightsRisk": 10, "overallRisk": 10, "governanceEpochDate": 1748736000, "compensationAsOfEpochDate": 1735603200, "executiveTeam": [], "maxAge": 86400, "priceHint": 2, "previousClose": 57.55, "open": 57.98, "dayLow": 56.1165, "dayHigh": 57.98, "regularMarketPreviousClose": 57.55, "regularMarketOpen": 57.98, "regularMarketDayLow": 56.1165, "regularMarketDayHigh": 57.98, "payoutRatio": 0.0, "beta": 1.213, "trailingPE": 42.044777, "forwardPE": 16.473684, "volume": 656033, "regularMarketVolume": 656033, "averageVolume": 1530208, "